{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Ubiquiti Networks |model=mFi mPower |revision=Pro |asin=B00HXT8IN2 |newegg=12K-017G-00002 |is_manuf=No |fcc_date=02/01/2013 |fcc_id=SWX-MPOWERP |ic_id=6545A-MPOWERP |type=network connected power strip,IoT hub |pwr_v=110-125 |pwr_amp=15 |pwr_conn=NEMA 5-15P |pwr_ac_hz=50/60 |cpu1_brand=Atheros |cpu1_model=AR9331 |cpu1_cspeed=400 |fla1=8 |fla1_brand=Macronix |fla1_model=MX25L6408EM2I-12G |ram1=32 |ram1_brand=Winbond |ram1_model=W9425G6JB-5 |wi1_chip1_brand=Atheros |wi1_chip1_model=AR9331;AR9331-AL1A; |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_ant_conn=U.FL |wi1_txchains=1 |wi1_rxchains=1 |wi1_sstreams=1 |eth_cpu=true |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=1 |addl_chips=Integrated Power Metering IC;Prolific;PL7223;;8;,,, 3-Line to 8-Line Decoder/Demultiplexer;TI;SN74LV138A;;2;,,, Quadruple Bus Buffer Gate w/ 3-State Output;TI;SN74LV125A;;1; |stock_boot=U-Boot |stock_os=Linux;2.6.32.29; |802dot11_protocols=bgn |default_ip=192.168.1.20 |default_user=ubnt |default_pass=ubnt |oui_eth=80:2A:A8 }} {{TagLine|Power Strip with Ethernet and Wi-Fi Connectivity}} :[https://dl.ubnt.com/guides/mfi/mFi_mPower_PRO_US_QSG.pdf Quick Start Guide]
"95.0900", "Rev.0 GP", and "801281" is silkscreened on the CPU board.
Documentation lists memory as 16MB but on-hand device and FCC photos show 32MB.
===Specifications=== *CPU: ''[[Atheros]]'' AR9331 @400MHz (MIPS 24K) *Storage: 8MB (NOR) Flash *Memory: 32MB (DDR) RAM *WiFi: 802.11b/g/n (1T1R) *Network: 1x Fast Ethernet port
